pageContext.claim: “How can the Rigged Witch Hunt proceed when it was started, influenced and worked on, for an extended period of time, by former FBI Agent/Lover Peter Strzok? Read his hate filled and totally biased Emails and the answer is clear!”
pageContext.analysis: FBI agent Peter Strzok sent anti-Trump text messages in 2016 and was criticized by the Justice Department's inspector general. But the IG report also found that no improper biases or considerations went into the FBI's decision making in 2016. In any case, Strzok worked on special counsel Robert Mueller's team in June and July 2017, months after the ongoing investigation began.
